* What 'Yes+Pin' means? the Add-In’s Sidebar can be 'pinned', that is, set to open automatically for relevant items you select, so you will not need to open it every time when browsing emails or meetings in your email client.
** Presently, due to a limitation in MS Outlook Mobile, in MS Outlook for Android/iOS the Add-In can be used with Office 365/Office.com accounts only. However, your data can be exchanged with Salesforce using {{ short_name }} sync (through auto-syncing or the custom "Salesforce Emails" folder).
!!! note "Note"
 If your email client is Microsoft Outlook for Windows, please make sure the latest version of MS Edge is installed in your system because it is used to render the Sidebar in Outlook
Browsers
Since {{ product_name }} is a cloud solution, if used via Outlook on the Web it can run in a browser. Please check browser's compatibility and update your browser to the latest version for the best experience with {{ product_name }}.




